<h3 data-start="4472" data-end="4492">R code structure</h3>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="4493" data-end="5064"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>R</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼ6"># 1. Load packages</span><br><span class="ͼe">library</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">tidyverse</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼe">library</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">car</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼe">library</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">emmeans</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># 2. Import data</span><br><span class="ͼe">df</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">read.csv</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼc">"treatment_biomarker_data.csv"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># 3. Clean data</span><br><span class="ͼe">df</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">df</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">%&gt;%</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">mutate</span><span>(</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼe">treatment</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">factor</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">treatment</span><span>),</span><br><span>    </span><span class="ͼe">sex</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">factor</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">sex</span><span>)</span><br><span>  ) </span><span class="ͼe">%&gt;%</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">drop_na</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">outcome</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">treatment</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">sex</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># 4. Fit interaction model</span><br><span class="ͼe">fit</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">lm</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">outcome</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">~</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">treatment</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">*</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">sex</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">data</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">df</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼe">summary</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">fit</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># 5. ANOVA table</span><br><span class="ͼe">Anova</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">fit</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">type</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼb">3</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># 6. Diagnostic plots</span><br><span class="ͼe">par</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">mfrow</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">c</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼb">2</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼb">2</span><span>))</span><br><span class="ͼe">plot</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">fit</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># 7. Post hoc comparisons if interaction/significant main effects</span><br><span class="ͼe">emmeans</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">fit</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">pairwise</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">~</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">treatment</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">|</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">sex</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
