<hr data-start="804" data-end="807">
<h1 data-start="809" data-end="859">Option 2 (Best for Oncology Research): SEER Data</h1>
<p data-start="860" data-end="957">Dataset: <strong data-start="869" data-end="957"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">SEER Program</span></span> from the <span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">National Cancer Institute</span></span></strong></p>
<p data-start="959" data-end="1043">This is <strong data-start="967" data-end="1005">the gold standard registry dataset</strong> used in thousands of oncology papers.</p>
<p data-start="1045" data-end="1053">Website:</p>
<p data-start="1055" data-end="1084"><a data-start="1055" data-end="1084" rel="noopener" target="_new" class="decorated-link" href="https://seer.cancer.gov/data/">https://seer.cancer.gov/data/<span aria-hidden="true" class="ms-0.5 inline-block align-middle leading-none"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" data-rtl-flip="" class="block h-[0.75em] w-[0.75em] stroke-current stroke-[0.75]"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#304883" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></span></a></p>
<p data-start="1086" data-end="1092">Steps:</p>
<ol data-start="1094" data-end="1238">
<li data-start="1094" data-end="1118">
<p data-start="1097" data-end="1118">Request access (free)</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1119" data-end="1144">
<p data-start="1122" data-end="1144">Download <strong data-start="1131" data-end="1144">SEER*Stat</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1145" data-end="1238">
<p data-start="1148" data-end="1170">Export variables like:</p>
<ul data-start="1174" data-end="1238">
<li data-start="1174" data-end="1191">
<p data-start="1176" data-end="1191">survival months</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1195" data-end="1209">
<p data-start="1197" data-end="1209">vital status</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1213" data-end="1220">
<p data-start="1215" data-end="1220">stage</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1224" data-end="1229">
<p data-start="1226" data-end="1229">age</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1233" data-end="1238">
<p data-start="1235" data-end="1238">sex</p>
</li>
</ul>
</li>
</ol>
<p data-start="1240" data-end="1245">Pros:</p>
<ul data-start="1246" data-end="1295">
<li data-start="1246" data-end="1273">
<p data-start="1248" data-end="1273">real cancer registry data</p>
</li>
<li data-start="1274" data-end="1295">
<p data-start="1276" data-end="1295">extremely respected</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1297" data-end="1302">Cons:</p>
<ul data-start="1303" data-end="1365">
<li data-start="1303" data-end="1337">
<p data-start="1305" data-end="1337">takes <strong data-start="1311" data-end="1337">1–2 days to get access</strong></p>
</li>
<li data-start="1338" data-end="1365">
<p data-start="1340" data-end="1365">slightly more complicated</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="1367" data-end="1424">This is an <strong data-start="1378" data-end="1423">excellent dataset once you're comfortable</strong>.</p>
<hr data-start="1426" data-end="1429">
<h1 data-start="1431" data-end="1504">Option 3 (Very Good for Survival Analysis Practice): Built-in R Dataset</h1>
<p data-start="1505" data-end="1649">You can start immediately using the dataset inside <strong data-start="1556" data-end="1597"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">R (programming language)</span></span></strong> from the <strong data-start="1607" data-end="1648"><span class="hover:entity-accent entity-underline inline cursor-pointer align-baseline"><span class="whitespace-normal">survival R package</span></span></strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1651" data-end="1676">Dataset: <strong data-start="1660" data-end="1676">lung dataset</strong></p>
<p data-start="1678" data-end="1746">This dataset contains survival information for lung cancer patients.</p>
<p data-start="1748" data-end="1762">Run this in R:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1764" data-end="1814"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>R</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼe">library</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">survival</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼe">data</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">lung</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼe">head</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">lung</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="1816" data-end="1834">Variables include:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="1836" data-end="1983" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="1836" data-end="1858"><tr data-start="1836" data-end="1858"><th data-start="1836" data-end="1847" data-col-size="sm" class="">Variable</th><th data-start="1847" data-end="1858" data-col-size="sm" class="">Meaning</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="1869" data-end="1983"><tr data-start="1869" data-end="1893"><td data-start="1869" data-end="1876" data-col-size="sm">time</td><td data-start="1876" data-end="1893" data-col-size="sm">survival time</td></tr><tr data-start="1894" data-end="1922"><td data-start="1894" data-end="1903" data-col-size="sm">status</td><td data-start="1903" data-end="1922" data-col-size="sm">survival status</td></tr><tr data-start="1923" data-end="1936"><td data-start="1923" data-end="1929" data-col-size="sm">age</td><td data-start="1929" data-end="1936" data-col-size="sm">age</td></tr><tr data-start="1937" data-end="1950"><td data-start="1937" data-end="1943" data-col-size="sm">sex</td><td data-start="1943" data-end="1950" data-col-size="sm">sex</td></tr><tr data-start="1951" data-end="1983"><td data-start="1951" data-end="1961" data-col-size="sm">ph.ecog</td><td data-start="1961" data-end="1983" data-col-size="sm">performance status</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 33px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<p data-start="1985" data-end="2081">You could simulate <strong data-start="2004" data-end="2020">stage groups</strong> or categorize other variables to practice survival modeling.</p>
<p data-start="2083" data-end="2088">Pros:</p>
<ul data-start="2089" data-end="2152">
<li data-start="2089" data-end="2107">
<p data-start="2091" data-end="2107">zero downloading</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2108" data-end="2152">
<p data-start="2110" data-end="2152">widely used for teaching survival analysis</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2154" data-end="2159">Cons:</p>
<ul data-start="2160" data-end="2201">
<li data-start="2160" data-end="2201">
<p data-start="2162" data-end="2201">doesn't include stage variable directly</p>
</li>
</ul>
<hr data-start="2203" data-end="2206">
<h1 data-start="2208" data-end="2263">What I recommend for your <strong data-start="2236" data-end="2263">first portfolio project</strong></h1>
<p data-start="2265" data-end="2276">Start with:</p>
<p data-start="2278" data-end="2307"><strong data-start="2278" data-end="2307">Option 1 (Kaggle dataset)</strong></p>
<p data-start="2309" data-end="2317">Because:</p>
<ul data-start="2318" data-end="2380">
<li data-start="2318" data-end="2330">
<p data-start="2320" data-end="2330">CSV format</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2331" data-end="2345">
<p data-start="2333" data-end="2345">easy to load</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2346" data-end="2363">
<p data-start="2348" data-end="2363">already cleaned</p>
</li>
<li data-start="2364" data-end="2380">
<p data-start="2366" data-end="2380">includes stage</p>
</li>
</ul>
<p data-start="2382" data-end="2415">Once you're comfortable, move to:</p>
<p data-start="2417" data-end="2450"><strong data-start="2417" data-end="2450">SEER → real registry research</strong></p>
<hr data-start="2452" data-end="2455">
<h1 data-start="2457" data-end="2499">Example of loading a Kaggle dataset in R</h1>
<p data-start="2501" data-end="2517">Once downloaded:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2519" data-end="2617"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>R</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼe">library</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">tidyverse</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼe">df</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">read.csv</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼc">"data/lung_cancer_survival.csv"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼe">head</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">df</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼe">summary</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">df</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2619" data-end="2666">Then continue with your survival analysis code.</p>
<hr data-start="2668" data-end="2671">
<h1 data-start="2673" data-end="2707">Important Tip for Your Portfolio</h1>
<p data-start="2709" data-end="2783">When using Kaggle or public datasets, include this section in your README:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2785" data-end="2979"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Dataset Source</span><br><br><span>This dataset was obtained from Kaggle and contains de-identified clinical information for lung cancer patients, including survival time, stage at diagnosis, age, and sex.</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2981" data-end="3064">That makes your project look <strong data-start="3010" data-end="3063">properly documented like a real research analysis</strong>.</p>
