<p data-start="1738" data-end="1795">If <strong data-start="1741" data-end="1753">p &lt; 0.05</strong>, survival differs significantly by stage.</p>
<hr data-start="1797" data-end="1800">
<h1 data-start="1802" data-end="1843">Step 5 — Cox proportional hazards model</h1>
<p data-start="1845" data-end="1872">Now estimate hazard ratios:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1874" data-end="1998"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>R</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼe">cox_model</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">coxph</span><span>(</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">surv_object</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">~</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Cancer_Stage</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">+</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Age</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">+</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Gender</span><span>,</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">data</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">lung_cancer_dataset</span><br><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼe">summary</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">cox_model</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2000" data-end="2019">This model answers:</p>
<blockquote data-start="2021" data-end="2108">
<p data-start="2023" data-end="2108">How much does stage increase the <strong data-start="2056" data-end="2075">hazard of death</strong>, controlling for age and gender?</p>
</blockquote>
<p data-start="2110" data-end="2133">Example interpretation:</p>
<div class="TyagGW_tableContainer"><div tabindex="-1" class="group TyagGW_tableWrapper flex flex-col-reverse w-fit"><table data-start="2135" data-end="2284" class="w-fit min-w-(--thread-content-width)"><thead data-start="2135" data-end="2167"><tr data-start="2135" data-end="2167"><th data-start="2135" data-end="2143" data-col-size="sm" class="">Stage</th><th data-start="2143" data-end="2167" data-col-size="sm" class="">Hazard Ratio Meaning</th></tr></thead><tbody data-start="2178" data-end="2284"><tr data-start="2178" data-end="2223"><td data-start="2178" data-end="2189" data-col-size="sm">Stage II</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="2189" data-end="2223">higher death risk than Stage I</td></tr><tr data-start="2224" data-end="2256"><td data-start="2224" data-end="2236" data-col-size="sm">Stage III</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="2236" data-end="2256">much higher risk</td></tr><tr data-start="2257" data-end="2284"><td data-start="2257" data-end="2268" data-col-size="sm">Stage IV</td><td data-col-size="sm" data-start="2268" data-end="2284">highest risk</td></tr></tbody></table><div class="sticky h-0 select-none end-(--thread-content-margin) self-end"><div class="absolute end-0 flex items-end" style="height: 33px;"><span class="" data-state="closed"><button aria-label="Copy table" class="hover:bg-token-bg-tertiary text-token-text-secondary my-1 rounded-sm p-1 transition-opacity group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:pointer-events-none group-[:not(:hover):not(:focus-within)]:opacity-0"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></span></div></div></div></div>
<hr data-start="2286" data-end="2289">
<h1 data-start="2291" data-end="2326">Step 6 — Clean hazard ratio table</h1>
<p data-start="2328" data-end="2332">Run:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2334" data-end="2396"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>R</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="c