<h1 data-start="1326" data-end="1348">4️⃣ Edit your README</h1>
<p data-start="1349" data-end="1398">Click your <strong data-start="1360" data-end="1373">README.md</strong> file and press <strong data-start="1389" data-end="1397">edit</strong>.</p>
<p data-start="1400" data-end="1426">Paste something like this:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1428" data-end="2256"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span># Lung Cancer Survival Analysis</span><br><br><span>## Overview</span><br><span>This project analyzes overall survival in lung cancer patients using Kaplan–Meier survival curves and Cox proportional hazards models.</span><br><br><span>## Research Question</span><br><span>Does stage at diagnosis affect overall survival in lung cancer patients?</span><br><br><span>## Dataset</span><br><span>The dataset includes 1,500 lung cancer patients with demographic, clinical, and survival variables.</span><br><br><span>Key variables:</span><br><span>- Cancer_Stage</span><br><span>- Survival_Months</span><br><span>- Survived</span><br><span>- Age</span><br><span>- Gender</span><br><br><span>## Methods</span><br><span>- Kaplan–Meier survival estimation</span><br><span>- Log-rank test</span><br><span>- Cox proportional hazards regression</span><br><br><span>## Results</span><br><span>Kaplan–Meier survival curves show significantly worse survival for later cancer stages (p &lt; 0.0001).  </span><br><span>Cox regression indicates progressively higher hazards of death with advancing stage at diagnosis.</span><br><br><span>## Tools</span><br><span>- R</span><br><span>- survival package</span><br><span>- survminer</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2258" data-end="2288">Then click <strong data-start="2269" data-end="2287">Commit changes</strong>.</p>
