<h1 data-start="1255" data-end="1300">Your script should look something like this</h1>
<p data-start="1302" data-end="1320">Example structure:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="1322" data-end="2229"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="sticky z-2 select-none top-(--sticky-padding-top)"><div class="flex w-full items-center justify-between py-1.5 ps-4 pe-1.5 font-sans md:ps-5 bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary"><div class="flex max-w-[75%] min-w-0 cursor-default items-center text-sm font-medium justify-self-start text-token-text-primary"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-sm me-2.5 shrink-0"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#e45ab3" fill="currentColor"></use></svg>R</div><div class="flex flex-row items-center gap-0.5 justify-self-end"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div></div></div><div class="pointer-events-none absolute inset-x-4 top-12 bottom-4"><div class="pointer-events-none sticky z-40 shrink-0 z-1!" style="top: calc(calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px) - 1px * 3); margin-bottom: calc(-4px); height: calc(4px); mask-image: linear-gradient(transparent 25%, white 75%);"><div class="sticky bg-token-border-light" style="top: calc(var(--sticky-padding-top) + 48px); height: 1px;"></div></div></div><div class="" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span class="ͼ6"># Lung Cancer Survival Analysis</span><br><span class="ͼ6"># Kaplan-Meier survival curves and Cox model</span><br><br><span class="ͼe">library</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">tidyverse</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼe">library</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">survival</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼe">library</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">survminer</span><span>)</span><br><span class="ͼe">library</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">broom</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># Load dataset</span><br><span class="ͼe">lung_cancer_dataset</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">read.csv</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼc">"lung_cancer_dataset.csv"</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># Create survival status variable</span><br><span class="ͼe">lung_cancer_dataset</span><span class="ͼ8">$</span><span class="ͼe">status</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">ifelse</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">lung_cancer_dataset</span><span class="ͼ8">$</span><span class="ͼe">Survived</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">==</span><span> </span><span class="ͼc">"No"</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼb">1</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼb">0</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># Create survival object</span><br><span class="ͼe">surv_object</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Surv</span><span>(</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">time</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">lung_cancer_dataset</span><span class="ͼ8">$</span><span class="ͼe">Survival_Months</span><span>,</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">event</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">lung_cancer_dataset</span><span class="ͼ8">$</span><span class="ͼe">status</span><br><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># Kaplan-Meier model</span><br><span class="ͼe">km_fit</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">survfit</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">surv_object</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">~</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Cancer_Stage</span><span>, </span><span class="ͼe">data</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">lung_cancer_dataset</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># Plot survival curves</span><br><span class="ͼe">ggsurvplot</span><span>(</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">km_fit</span><span>,</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">data</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">lung_cancer_dataset</span><span>,</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">pval</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼb">TRUE</span><span>,</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">conf.int</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼb">TRUE</span><span>,</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">risk.table</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼb">TRUE</span><br><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># Cox proportional hazards model</span><br><span class="ͼe">cox_model</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">&lt;-</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">coxph</span><span>(</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">surv_object</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">~</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Cancer_Stage</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">+</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Age</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">+</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">Gender</span><span>,</span><br><span>  </span><span class="ͼe">data</span><span> </span><span class="ͼ8">=</span><span> </span><span class="ͼe">lung_cancer_dataset</span><br><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼe">summary</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">cox_model</span><span>)</span><br><br><span class="ͼ6"># Check proportional hazards</span><br><span class="ͼe">cox.zph</span><span>(</span><span class="ͼe">cox_model</span><span>)</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<hr data-start="2231" data-end="2234">
<h1 data-start="2236" data-end="2258">Then save the script</h1>
<p data-start="2260" data-end="2266">Press:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2268" data-end="2287"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>Command + S</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2289" data-end="2300">Save it as:</p>
<pre class="overflow-visible! px-0!" data-start="2302" data-end="2329"><div class="relative w-full my-4"><div class=""><div class="relative"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0"><div class="h-full min-h-0 min-w-0" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"><div class="border border-token-border-light border-radius-3xl corner-superellipse/1.1 rounded-3xl"><div class="h-full w-full border-radius-3xl bg-token-bg-elevated-secondary corner-superellipse/1.1 overflow-clip rounded-3xl lxnfua_clipPathFallback"><div class="pointer-events-none absolute end-1.5 top-1 z-2 md:end-2 md:top-1"><button class="flex gap-1 items-center select-none pointer-events-auto py-2 text-sm font-medium hover:bg-black/5 dark:hover:bg-white/10 size-9 rounded-full px-2" aria-label="Copy" data-state="closed"><svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" width="20" height="20" aria-hidden="true" class="icon-md"><use href="/cdn/assets/sprites-core-eri7ssmm.svg#ce3544" fill="currentColor"></use></svg></button></div><div class="pt-3" style="transform: none;"><div class="relative z-0 flex max-w-full"><div id="code-block-viewer" dir="ltr" class="q9tKkq_viewer cm-editor z-10 light:cm-light dark:cm-light flex h-full w-full flex-col items-stretch ͼ5 ͼj"><div class="cm-scroller"><div class="cm-content q9tKkq_readonly"><span>survival_analysis.R</span></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div></div><div class=""><div class="" style="width: 100%; transform: none;"></div></div></div></div></div></pre>
<p data-start="2331" data-end="2407">Now it will appear in your <strong data-start="2358" data-end="2373">Files panel</strong>, and you can upload it to GitHub.</p>
